            "badge": "🗎",
            "text": [
                "Domestia Player Choice is part of the Domestia mod family.",
                "",
                "The Domestia Player Choice Digest and the Domestia Player Choice Board are designed as in-game publishing devices for server communities.",
                "",
                "They allow an administrator, editor, or other responsible player to share important world events, server news, technical notes, travel reports, announcements, and other useful information with everyone on the server.",
                "",
                "The Digest is a personal handheld reader. The Board is a public notice device intended for shared spaces, settlements, hubs, and other places where players naturally gather.",
                "",
                "Together, they provide a simple way to turn server communication into part of the world itself, instead of leaving it outside the game in chat logs, Discord channels, or external pages.",
                "",
                "All visual content, menu structure, text sections, links, and page images can be replaced through a resource pack."
            ]
